snippet.title: Aggelos - Launch Trailer - Steam
snippet.description:
Aggelos is a wonderful homage to Wonderboy - staying true to the aesthetic, but modernising the mechanics with Metroidvania leanings! 

Aggelos is OUT NOW on Steam - https://store.steampowered.com/app/717310/Aggelos/

Come chat to us on our PQube Discord server! https://discord.gg/xHS7MnU
